=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Terni</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 21 mar, ore 19:00, &#8220;Cosa c&#8217;è dietro Internet?&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-terni/events/299746071\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Catania</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 21 mar, ore 19:00, &#8220;Ultime Novità di WordPress e Full Site Editing&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/meetup-wordpress-catania/events/299456994\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vicenza</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mar 26 mar, ore 19:00, &#8220;Freelance con WordPress: il valore del nostro lavoro con l&#8217;Open Source&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-vicenza/events/299833421\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Treviso</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 28 mar, ore 19:30, &#8220;Ask Me Anything, marzo 2024&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/treviso-wordpress-meetup/events/299777254\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-dark-blueberry-color has-blueberry-3-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-extra-large-font-size\">… articolo in aggiornamento…</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2024/03/tutti-i-meetup-di-marzo-2024/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_