Torino</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 18 gen, ore 18:30, &#8220;FSE: da dove comincio?&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-torino/events/298070742\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Terni</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 18 gen, ore 19:00, &#8220;Scopriamo l&#8217;intelligenza Artificiale Generativa&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-terni/events/298417612\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Zagarolo</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 19 gen, ore 18:00, &#8220;Com&#8217;è fatto WordPress?&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/zagarolo-wordpress-meetup/events/298281295\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Napoli</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 25 gen, ore 18:00, &#8220;WP come boost per nuove sfide Tecnologiche&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-napoli-meetup/events/298523961\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Treviso</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 25 gen, ore 19:30, &#8220;Guida pratica al Full Site Editing&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/treviso-wordpress-meetup/events/298302612\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Roma</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 26 gen, ore 18:00, &#8220;Verso il Full Site Editing e oltre!&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/romawordpress/events/298188839\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Avezzano</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mar 30 gen, ore 18:00, &#8220;Realizziamo un sito personalizzato usando l’installazione base di WordPress.&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/avezzano-wordpress-meetup/events/298508988\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2024/01/tutti-i-meetup-di-gennaio-2024/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:106:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tutti i meetup di dicembre 2023\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2023/12/tutti-i-meetup-di-dicembre-2023/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2023/12/tutti-i-meetup-di-dicembre-2023/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 05 Dec 2023 17:41:42 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"